SUMMARY:Bloomington Community Farmers’ Market
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260404T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260404T123000
UID:ai1ec-147868-94592@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Market goers find a wide assortment of goods from the farm and
  field\, including fruits and vegetables\, eggs\, meats and cheeses\, hone
 y\, seasonal flowers\, and annual and perennial plants. Food and beverage 
 artisans provide a tasteful variety of drinks\, pastries\, and savory dish
 es. This weekly gathering provides opportunities for individuals to connec
 t with their community in meaningful ways and support local farmers and sm
 all businesses.
LOCATION:Showers Common\, 401 N. Morton St\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/bloomington-community-farmers-market-10/?instan
 ce_id=94592
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
