UID:ai1ec-147886-94636@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Head for downtown Martinsville on Thursdays\, April through Oc
 tober for the weekly Cruise-in on the Square! Vehicles of all kinds are we
 lcome – antiques\, classics\, hot rods\, trucks\, motorcycles\, tractors
 \, etc. The weekly cruise-in will be held on Thursdays from 5 to 9 pm each
  week. Come out for a fun evening in downtown Martinsville as you view the
  participating vehicles and enjoy dinner and shopping on the square. The c
 ruise-in will be located on the east side of the square along Jefferson St
 reet\, from Pike to Jackson Streets.
LOCATION:Morgan County Courthouse Square\, 180 Main Street\, Martinsville
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/martinsville-cruise-in-on-the-square/?instance_
 id=94636
